    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on the 'harm principle' part? Like, how would someone argue that stuff like misinformation or hate speech doesn't meet that 'demonstrable harm' threshold? I want to make sure my argument is airtight against people who say regulation is necessary for safety.",
